```
# Rust-specific ignores
target/
Cargo.lock

# Dependencies
vendor/

# Build artifacts
**/*.rs.bk
**/*.rlib

# Logs and temp files
*.log
*.tmp

# Environment
.env
.env.local
.env.*

# Editors
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo

# OS generated files
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# Coverage reports
coverage/
htmlcov/
.coverage

# Cache directories
**/__pycache__/
**/.mypy_cache/
**/.pytest_cache/
```